                p #[strong Premium account]  – you can upgrade to a premium account at any time. For a small annual fee of £99, you can earn points on every £1 spent and redeem for 1 Avios and 1% cashback. If you spend £5000 in the first 3 months, you will receive 20,000 bonus points. 
                p #[strong Supplementary cards] – depending on the card option you choose, you can get up to 20 supplementary cards for your employees and partners. You can set a credit limit for each card and freeze them anytime.
